Exceptional Formulation

Emphasising inclusivity, the vegan protein supplement is not only dairy- and nut-free but also soy- and gluten-free, catering to a diverse range of dietary preferences and restrictions. So, whether you're lactose intolerant, allergic to nuts, avoiding soy, or gluten-sensitive, this vegan protein supplement aims to accommodate various dietary needs.

High-quality Ingredients

Featuring a potent combination of pea protein isolate and organic pumpkin seed protein, this supplement delivers impressive performance. Formulated with all essential amino acids, it provides a comprehensive protein profile to support your body's requirements. Its easy digestibility, achieved through the exclusive use of natural ingredients, ensures a smooth experience.

![](https://rukminim2.flixcart.com/image/200/200/xif0q/icons/original-PSLG6Z3WAG77HYXG_3.jpg)

Diverse Benefits

This vegan protein supplement offers numerous advantages, ensuring optimal purity with its natural ingredients and allergen-free composition. It actively promotes active growth, catering to a broad audience. So, whether you're lactose intolerant or aiming to prevent muscle loss, this supplement addresses your needs. Beyond that, it goes the extra mile to enhance skin and hair health, boost immunity, facilitate post-workout recovery, and aid in weight loss and management. Additionally, this supplement promotes heart health, fortifies bones, enhances gut health by minimising bloating, and regulates appetite while providing essential nutrition.

![](https://rukminim2.flixcart.com/image/200/200/xif0q/icons/original-PSLG6Z3WAG77HYXG_4.jpg)

High Versatility

Thanks to its chocolate flavour and versatile nature, this vegan protein seamlessly integrates into your daily routine. Whether blended with water, plant-based milk, shakes, or smoothies, it offers a hassle-free way to meet your protein requirements. It's also versatile in baking, allowing you to incorporate it into your preferred cookie and cake recipes.
